OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fclearing southwards this evening,
OL,7,Fgiving a few heavier bursts in places.
OL,8,FSkies clearing overnight with perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd isolated shower. Turning cold
OL,10,Fwith a rural frost developing,
OL,11,Fespecially in Cumbria. Breezy this
OL,12,Fevening but winds falling light
OL,13,Fovernight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FA much brighter day with a
OL,16,Fmixture of sunny periods and
OL,17,Foccasional cloudier spells. Staying
OL,18,Fgenerally dry until after dark. Cooler
OL,19,Fthan on Wednesday but pleasantly warm
OL,20,Fin the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
