OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRather
OL,6,Funsettled over the Easter weekend with
OL,7,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,8,FWindy at times with gales and
OL,9,Fdisruptive winds possible on Saturday.
OL,10,FSome warm sunshine at times too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
